5th Avenue, north from Fourth Street, underneath the B.M.T. elevated. Note the stairway to the "El" station, at Third Street. View 2 shows the "El" station at Third Street, seen across the James J. Byrne Memorial Park and Playground at the N.W. corner of Fifth Avenue and Fourth Street.

P.L. Sperr
June 14, 1940
Views 1,2
